MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: THE STATION IS LOCATED ON THE TIMPANOGOS CAVE UTAH-UTAH CO. 7.5 MINUTE SERIES (TOPOGRAPHIC) QUADRANGLE.  THE SITE IS THE SURFACE WATER THAT PERCOLATES INTO CHIMES CHAMBER AND FORMS CHIMES CHAMBER DRIP WHICH IS LOCATED INSIDE THE TIMPANOGOS CAVE NATIONAL MONUMENT BOUNDARIES.
